# Leptos Marketplace - Project Intelligence for AI

## 🎯 Project Overview

Full-stack Rust marketplace management system integrating with Wildberries and Ozon, powered by 1C:UT11 data.

### UI Design Reference

**bolt-mpi-ui-redesign** (`E:\dev\bolt\bolt-mpi-ui-redesign`) - эталонный проект для стилей UI:
- Модальные окна, формы, компоненты
- Стили: `public/themes/base.css`, `dark.css`, `light.css`
- Ключевые размеры: input height 30px, padding 5px 12px

## 🏗️ Architecture Quick Reference

### Tech Stack

- **Frontend**: Leptos 0.8 (Rust → WASM)
- **Backend**: Axum (async Rust)
- **Database**: SQLite (marketplace.db)
- **Architecture**: DDD + Vertical Slice Architecture (VSA)
- **Workspace**: 3 crates (contracts, backend, frontend)

### Critical Structure

```
crates/
├── contracts/    # Shared DTOs & types between frontend/backend
├── backend/      # Axum server, domain logic, repositories
└── frontend/     # Leptos UI components
```

## 📦 Naming System (CRITICAL)

This project uses indexed naming for features:

### Aggregates: `a001-a499` (Domain entities)

Реализованы: a001–a026 (все в `crates/*/src/domain/aNNN_xxx/`)

### UseCases: `u501-u999` (Operations)

- `u501_import_from_ut` - Import from 1C:UT11
- `u502_import_from_ozon` - Ozon integration
- `u503_import_from_yandex` - Yandex Market integration
- `u504_import_from_wildberries` - WB integration
- `u505_match_nomenclature` - Nomenclature matching
- `u506_import_from_lemanapro` - LemanaPro integration

### Projections: `p900-p999` (Read models/analytics)

Реализованы: p900–p911 (все в `crates/*/src/projections/pNNN_xxx/`)

### System Tables: `sys_*` (System infrastructure)

- `sys_users` - User accounts
- `sys_refresh_tokens` - JWT refresh tokens
- `sys_audit_log` - Audit trail
- `sys_settings` - System-wide settings

**File Structure Example:**

```
crates/backend/src/domain/a001_connection_1c/
├── mod.rs
├── service.rs       # Business logic orchestration
└── repository.rs    # Database CRUD operations

crates/contracts/src/domain/a001_connection_1c/
├── mod.rs
├── aggregate.rs     # AggregateRoot implementation
├── metadata.json    # METADATA SOURCE (edit this)
└── metadata_gen.rs  # AUTO-GENERATED (don't edit)

crates/backend/src/system/          # System functionality (auth, users, etc.)
├── auth/
│   ├── jwt.rs
│   ├── password.rs
│   ├── middleware.rs
│   └── extractor.rs
├── users/
│   ├── repository.rs
│   └── service.rs
└── handlers/
    ├── auth.rs
    └── users.rs

crates/frontend/src/domain/a001_connection_1c/ui/
├── list/           # List view
└── details/        # Details view

crates/frontend/src/system/         # System UI (login, user management)
├── auth/
│   ├── context.rs
│   ├── guard.rs
│   └── api.rs
├── users/ui/
│   ├── list/
│   └── details/
└── pages/
    └── login.rs
```

## ⚠️ General Ledger — Отдельная независимая система

**General Ledger — это НЕ domain-агрегат.** Это независимая подсистема бухгалтерского учёта.

**Правило:** весь код General Ledger находится в `src/general_ledger/` во всех крейтах:

```
crates/contracts/src/general_ledger/    ← типы, DTOs, plan счетов, виды оборотов
crates/backend/src/general_ledger/      ← repository, service, account_registry, turnover_registry
crates/frontend/src/general_ledger/     ← api.rs (API-клиент), ui/ (list, details, turnovers)
```

**НЕ делать:**
- ❌ `crates/frontend/src/domain/general_ledger/` — неправильно
- ❌ Любое размещение в `domain/` — неправильно

**Импорт в frontend:**
- `lib.rs` → `pub mod general_ledger;` (на верхнем уровне, рядом с domain, projections)
- `registry.rs` → `use crate::general_ledger::ui::{GeneralLedgerPage, ...};`

---

## 🔑 Critical Patterns

### 1. Field Metadata System (See: memory-bank/architecture/metadata-system.md)

- **metadata.json**: Single source of truth for aggregate structure
- **metadata_gen.rs**: Auto-generated by `build.rs` (DO NOT EDIT)
- **AggregateRoot trait**: `entity_metadata_info()` and `field_metadata()` methods
- **AI context**: `ai.description`, `ai.questions`, `ai.related` for LLM chat

### 2. Domain Layer Rules (See: memory-bank/architecture/domain-layer-architecture.md)

- **repository.rs**: ONLY database CRUD, NO business logic
- **service.rs**: Orchestrates operations, calls validators, business rules
- **aggregate.rs**: Data structure + simple instance methods + AggregateRoot impl
- **events.rs**: Complex validation/lifecycle handlers (optional, only if needed)

### 3. Lifecycle Events (1C-style)

```rust
// Create/Update flow:
1. validate()       // Can block operation
2. before_write()   // Can modify data
3. service logic    // Business rules
4. repository::save()

// Delete flow:
1. before_delete()  // Can block operation
2. repository::soft_delete()
```

### 4. Layer Communication

```
Handlers → Service → Repository → Database
         ↘ UseCases (for multi-aggregate operations)
```

**DON'T**: Call repository directly from handlers
**DO**: Always go through service layer

## 🚨 Environment-Specific Rules

### Windows Environment

- **Shell**: PowerShell (NOT bash)
- **Command chaining**: Use semicolons `;` or separate commands, NEVER use `&&`
- **Node.js**: Use `pnpm` (not npm/yarn)

### Development Commands

```powershell
# Backend (миграции применяются автоматически при старте)
cargo run --bin backend

# Frontend (development)
trunk serve --port 8080

# Frontend (production build)
trunk build --release

# Добавить новую миграцию схемы БД:
# 1. Создать migrations/0002_description.sql
# 2. cargo run --bin backend  <- применится автоматически

# Проверить текущие миграции:
# sqlite3 marketplace.db "SELECT version, description FROM _sqlx_migrations"
```

## 📊 Database Patterns

### Table Naming

- Aggregates: `a001_connection_1c_database`
- UseCases history: `u501_import_history`
- Projections: `p904_sales_data`
- System: `sys_users`, `sys_tasks`, `sys_settings`

### Migration System (CRITICAL)

Изменения схемы ТОЛЬКО через `migrations/NNNN_description.sql`. Никогда не добавлять SQL в `db.rs`.

```
migrations/
├── 0001_baseline_schema.sql   <- полная исходная схема (40+ таблиц)
├── 0002_...                   <- новые изменения
└── archive/                   <- старые migrate_*.sql (история)
```

Трекинг в `_sqlx_migrations`. Применяется автоматически при `cargo run --bin backend`.

## 🎨 Frontend Patterns

### Component Structure

```
domain/{feature}/ui/
├── list/
│   └── mod.rs       # List view with table
└── details/
    └── mod.rs       # Details/edit form
```

### Common Utilities

- `shared/list_utils.rs` - Table sorting, filtering helpers
- `shared/table_utils.rs` - Column resize with localStorage persistence
- `shared/date_utils.rs` - Date formatting
- `layout/center/tabs/tabs.rs` - Tab management

### Styling

- CSS in `frontend/styles/3-components/`
- Use existing table classes, form patterns
- Consistent UI: tabs, filters, date pickers

### Frontend Page Standards (CRITICAL)

- **All pages MUST follow BEM + Thaw UI standards**
- See: `memory-bank/architecture/frontend-page-standards.md` for complete specification
- Container: ALWAYS use `class="page"` (NOT "content")
- Header: ALWAYS use `page__header` with BEM children (NOT "page-header")
- Tables: Use Thaw Table OR BEM classes (NO plain `<table>` without classes)
- Reference implementations: `a002_organization`, `a012_wb_sales`
- **Automated audit available:** Use skill "audit page [name]" or see `.cursor/skills/audit-page-bem-thaw/`

### List Standard (IMPORTANT)

- See: `memory-bank/architecture/list-standard.md` for complete specification
- Эталон: `a012_wb_sales` - серверная пагинация, resize колонок, чекбоксы
- Все списки должны использовать серверную пагинацию (offset/limit)

## 🔐 Authentication System

- **JWT-based**: Access tokens (24h) + Refresh tokens (90 days)
- **Multi-user**: Stored in `sys_users` table
- **First run**: Auto-creates `admin/admin` user
- **Middleware**: `system::auth::middleware::require_auth` and `require_admin`
- **Frontend**: AuthProvider context, RequireAuth/RequireAdmin guards
- **Tokens**: Stored in localStorage on frontend

